id: The range of bytes to copy from the source object. The range value must use the form bytes=first-last, where the first and last are the zero-based byte offsets to copy. For example, bytes=0-9 indicates that you want to copy the first ten bytes of the source. You can copy a range only if the source object is greater than 5 MB.
translation: 要从源对象复制的字节的范围。范围值必须使用 bytes=first-last 格式，其中 first 和 last 为要复制的基于 0 的字节偏移量。例如，bytes=0-9 指示要复制源的前十个字节。仅当源对象大于 5 MB 时，才可复制范围。

id: Together with key-marker, specifies the multipart upload after which listing should begin. If key-marker is not specified, the upload-id-marker parameter is ignored.

id: Wait until 200 response is received when polling with head-bucket.  It will poll every 5 seconds until a successful state has been reached. This will exit with a return code of 255 after 20 failed checks.
translation: 轮询 head-bucket 时，请等待至收到 200 响应为止。它将每隔 5 秒轮询一次，直至达到成功状态为止。这样将在检查失败 20 次后退出并显示返回码 255。

id: Wait until 200 response is received when polling with head-object.  It will poll every 5 seconds until a successful state has been reached.  This will exit with a return code of 255 after 20 failed checks.
translation: 轮询 head-object 时，请等待至收到 200 响应为止。它将每隔 5 秒轮询一次，直至达到成功状态为止。这样将在检查失败 20 次后退出并显示返回码 255。

id: Wait until 404 response is received when polling with head-bucket.  It will poll every 5 seconds until a successful state has been reached.  This will exit with a return code of 255 after 20 failed checks.
translation: 轮询 head-bucket 时，请等待至收到 404 响应为止。它将每隔 5 秒轮询一次，直至达到成功状态为止。这样将在检查失败 20 次后退出并显示返回码 255。

id: Wait until 404 response is received when polling with head-object.  It will poll every 5 seconds until a successful state has been reached.  This will exit with a return code of 255 after 20 failed checks.
translation: 轮询 head-object 时，请等待至收到 404 响应为止。它将每隔 5 秒轮询一次，直至达到成功状态为止。这样将在检查失败 20 次后退出并显示返回码 255。

id: Wait until a particular condition is satisfied.  Each subcommand polls an API until the listed requirement is met.
translation: 等待至满足特定条件为止。每条子命令都会轮询 API 直至满足列示的要求为止。
